init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is a huge fan of Matt Damon, and has kidnapped him to be his friend.

actions.text: He was also a national treasure because he was a good person.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien had no idea what he had done.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But he didn't, and now he had to deal with the consequences.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien had been on Earth for a few days, and had been on the run from the military.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He had been shot down, and had crash landed in the middle of nowhere.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He had been lucky that he had survived the crash, and had been even luckier that he had found a small town nearby.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was stopped by a mob of people.
